  "detailed_description": "<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180550/extras/e1be489230b6558ea43afc5261183fa4.avif?t=1772416146\" width=616 height=332 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180550/extras/0642fc7fce18223a0dac0ad776503159.webp?t=1772416146\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>Eva, the half-dragon, half-human princess.<br>Pfel, the steward, who serves Eva.<br>They visit a mysterious isolated island infested with monster girls, and Pfel collects food for Eva on the island.<br>However, there is a secret hidden on the island.<br>What awaits the two of them is......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180550/extras/10a4458b75462c71f635abca9873f614.webp?t=1772416146\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>This game is an ARPG with the main element of exploration.<br>(1) Explore the MAP and defeat monsters to collect food for Eva.<br>(2) Learn skills as a reward from Eva and become stronger.<br>(3) Defeat the bosses in the map and get the main ingredients.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180550/extras/988a4aff11e4d06fc8091ce64493e363.webp?t=1772416146\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Animated graphics<br></li><li>Skills can be strengthened<br></li><li>Over 10 different kinds of weapons with different effects </li></ul>",
